{"tid":1277961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自由時報社會新聞】中心衝 強化玻璃擊破器","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T10:41:27.000Z","uid":34394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8702b33dace29d44a6866b152ac15e7f28adcef4","tid":1277961,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"中心衝 強化玻璃擊破器<br />\n2010-05-01<br />\n<br />\n形狀類似螺絲起子，與原子筆大小無異的中心衝（又稱強化玻璃擊破器），由於尖端鎢鋼材質、硬度高、使用又簡單，只要用力下壓便可擊碎物體，這種利用「反作用」原理的精密工具，接觸的材質越硬，產生的反作用力越大；如用於強化玻璃，則立刻產生放射狀破裂，大多用於鑽洞前的定位工具，因體積小、破壞力強，成為消防救難人員破門救災隨身裝備。 （記者陳恩惠）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/society/paper/392119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fpaper%2F392119&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=484ed6db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/society/paper/392119</a><br />\n<br />\n逃生必備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f571135b7cb48a296dc38a43c80a60b745881dd","tid":1277961,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:27:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0173a0d88bfb3d6a7aa47d5cda2c87c129b759b6","tid":1277961,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"而家好多商場都用強化玻璃，萬一火燭走唔到焗死點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有呢支野就唔怕啦"},{"pid":"64c4d94121f70aa8da15c32a54f2e55d2c2bb32d","tid":1277961,"uid":34394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%A1%9B%E7%88%BE%E5%BA%B7%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=0ff20cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%A1%9B%E7%88%BE%E5%BA%B7%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n唔係吹水，台灣就係咁死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衛爾康西餐廳二樓，朝往台中港路方向的窗口，使用整片式強化玻璃落地窗，窗上有重擊痕跡，研判是顧客用椅子之類的重物試圖擊破逃生，但未熟悉擊破強化玻璃的要領（正確方式應為敲擊玻璃的四角，而非拍打玻璃的正面），而無法順利逃出。而根據倖存者及台中市消防局勤務中心主任馮明勇的說法，第一塊玻璃未被敲破，第二塊玻璃則被成功敲破，有部分顧客從二樓跳出而得以倖存，但背部均受到明顯灼傷。<br />\n<br />\n大家要有呢啲實用知識知道點樣求生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f72f22b35bfa0fec109e5302abf922c5324dabf","tid":1277961,"uid":262522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:38:18.000Z","msg":"香港五金鋪叫punch(好似平時我地叫sofa咁)<br />\n叫同音字架<br />\n未聽過人叫中心衝<br />\n<br />\n你講話鑽鐵用來定位嘅，多數收埋無擺出來。"},{"pid":"c4c11ae6b7201dca90dfcd09fb6624a939caebab","tid":1277961,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"唔係簡單既強化玻璃黎<br />\n中間夾膠"}]}